ice\"><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> online business service</a> or by calling the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> helpline.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You won&rsquo;t need to give the pupil&rsquo;s details when you book. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> helpline</strong></p>\n\n<p>0300 200 1122<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Confirming the pupil&rsquo;s details</h3>\n\n<p>You must confirm the details of the pupil taking the test by 4pm a full working day before the test, eg by 4pm on Wednesday if the test is on Friday. </p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can do this using the <a href=\"/dsa-online-business-service\" title=\"DSA online business service\"><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> online business service</a>, or by phone or email.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Sundays and public holidays do not count as working days.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> helpline</strong></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#098;&#111;&#111;&#107;&#105;&#110;&#103;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#098;&#111;&#111;&#107;&#105;&#110;&#103;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n<strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 200 1122<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 200 1155<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Cancel or change a test</h3>\n\n<p>To cancel or change a test, use the <a href=\"/dsa-online-business-service\" title=\"DSA online business service\"><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> online business service</a> or phone <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> helpline</strong></p>\n\