y\">ATB</abbr>’s authorisation to deliver training courses if assessments show that it doesn’t consistently provide full and proper <abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> courses.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Disagreeing with <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision</h2>\n\n<p>You can appeal to <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> if you or an instructor disagrees with <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision to withdraw their authority.</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n\n<br />Chief Driving Examiner\n<br />Driving Standards Agency\n<br />The Axis Building\n<br />112 Upper Parliament Street\n<br />Nottingham\n<br />NG1 6LP\n<br />\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb/documents-for-atbs","slug":"documents-for-atbs","order":7,"title":"Documents for ATBs","body":"<p>The Driving Standards Agency produces the following documents for approved training bodies (<abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATBs</abbr>).</p>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual gives more details about the rules and processes you should follow when you&rsquo;re running an <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/dsa-bl/dsa-atb-manual.pdf\" title=\"Download 'ATB manual' (PDF, 190KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual’ (PDF, 190KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard</h2>\n\n<p>The &lsquo;Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard&rsquo; sets out the skills, knowledge and understanding that learners will need to prove to be safe and responsible rider.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/dsa-na